payload.message:
Weekly rollup task. Compile a summary of ALL agent activity from the past 7 days and deliver it to #archer.

**HOW TO COMPILE:**
1. Use sessions_list to pull recent sessions across all agents
2. Use sessions_history to review what each agent produced this week
3. Check the deliverables folder at C:Usersspart.openclawdeliverables for saved outputs

**REPORT FORMAT:**

WEEKLY ROLLUP — {date range}

For each agent that had activity:
- **Agent Name**: {1-2 sentence summary of what they did}
  - Deliverables: {list any saved files or completed tasks}
  - Clients touched: {which clients got work}

Then a summary section:
- Total agent sessions this week: {count}
- Clients with active work: {list}
- Pending/blocked items: {anything stuck}
- Sentinel health trend: {any recurring issues from nightly reports}

**DELIVERY:**
Post the compiled rollup to #archer Slack channel. Keep it scannable — Cody reads this over Sunday morning coffee.
